{"arkId":"cl010117711","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010117711","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre ronde \u00e0 double bo\u00eetier assortie d\u0027une ch\u00e2telaine","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre ronde \u00e0 double bo\u00eetier assortie d\u0027une ch\u00e2telaine"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XV (1715-1774) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : vers 1768 - 1770","currentLocation":"Sully, [OArt] Salle 614 - Galerie Louis XV, Vitrine 8","room":"Salle 614, Aile Aile Sully, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1768,"endYear":1770,"imprecision":"vers","text":"3e quart du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Ellicott, Edward","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1791","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 8606","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Montre ronde ; fond du bo\u00eetier form\u00e9 d\u0027une calotte en agate d\u00e9cor\u00e9e d\u0027une applique florale en \u00e9meraudes, rubis, saphirs et diamant ; pourtour orn\u00e9 de quatre m\u00e9daillons en en agate rehauss\u00e9s de rubis, \u00e9meraudes entour\u00e9s de volutes, guirlandes fleuries en or grav\u00e9 et partiellement ajour\u00e9es. Lunette d\u00e9cor\u00e9e de quatre m\u00e9daillons ovales en agate s\u00e9par\u00e9s par des cartouches \u00e0 rinceaux reperc\u00e9s ; poussoir enrichi d\u0027un rubis. Bo\u00eetier int\u00e9rieur en or poli, b\u00e9li\u00e8re orn\u00e9e de deux feuilles d\u0027acanthe. Cadran \u00e0 chiffres arabes et romains. Mouvement dot\u00e9 d\u0027un \u00e9chappement \u00e0 roue de rencontre, arr\u00eat de la cha\u00eene reperc\u00e9 de rinceaux. Disque du coq reperc\u00e9 de fins rinceaux asym\u00e9triques, son pied grav\u00e9 de rinceaux non ajour\u00e9s, talon orn\u00e9 d\u0027un mascaron. Ch\u00e2telaine compos\u00e9e de quatre plaques d\u0027agate d\u00e9cor\u00e9es d\u0027appliques florales compos\u00e9s de rubis, \u00e9meraudes, saphirs, diamant. Un cachet \u00e0 clef non grav\u00e9 et une clef \u00e0 manivelle accroch\u00e9s \u00e0 la plaque sup\u00e9rieure.","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; W B (deux fois)\r ; Signature : \r ; cadran sign\u00e9 : ELLICOTT \/ LONDON ; cache-poussi\u00e8re et platine du mouvement sign\u00e9s : Ellicot \/ London \/ 6247","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"4,1","displayDimension":"4,1 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2,1","displayDimension":"2,1 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"3,4","displayDimension":"3,4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2,1","displayDimension":"2,1 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":4,"note":""},{"type":"Longueur","value":"14","displayDimension":"14 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":5,"note":""},{"type":"Longueur","value":"19,6","displayDimension":"19,6 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":6,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : or\r\nMat\u00e9riau : agate\r\nTechnique : techniques m\u00e9tal (orf\u00e8vrerie)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : pierre pr\u00e9cieuse = pierres pr\u00e9cieuse